room_title: Escape room "The Haunted Mansion" by Panic In The Woods in Nashville
room_address: 2131 Joe Brown Rd, Spring Hill, TN 37174
room_description: You have been summoned to the Lockwood Mansion for the reading of Edmond Lockwood's last will and testament. Listed as one of the long lost relatives to receive an inheritance of a priceless necklace, you are locked in the mansion with one hour to find the necklace and the key to the way out before unexplained things happen.
